  "detailed_description": "PixelForces.io is a challenging 3D shooting online game. You can choose from five different multiplayer modes and maps and customize your character. The environment is structured like a vertical maze with trampolines. You can create a room to play, or enter in an already created room. Enjoy!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nFeatures:<br />\r\n• Five multiplayer game modes: RPG, Deathmatch, Team Deathmatch, Explore, and Battle Royale<br />\r\n• 5 amazing and unique maps with trampoline platforms<br />\r\n• Room options: max players, private, night toggle<br />\r\n• 12 character skins",
  "about_the_game": "PixelForces.io is a challenging 3D shooting online game. You can choose from five different multiplayer modes and maps and customize your character. The environment is structured like a vertical maze with trampolines. You can create a room to play, or enter in an already created room. Enjoy!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nFeatures:<br />\r\n• Five multiplayer game modes: RPG, Deathmatch, Team Deathmatch, Explore, and Battle Royale<br />\r\n• 5 amazing and unique maps with trampoline platforms<br />\r\n• Room options: max players, private, night toggle<br />\r\n• 12 character skins",
